TI  - ON MEMES: A BRIEF INTRODUCTION TO MEMETICA, OR A CONTEMPORARY RHETORIC OF INFORMATION
PY  - 2023
T2  - Cosmos and History
VL  - 19
IS  - 1
SP  - 158
